40
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:57,360
...Chopper Man!

41
00:02:58,400 --> 00:03:07,240
"Go, Chopper Man!
Protect the TV Station on the Beach"

42
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:10,120
I don't want to hear about no Chopper Man!

43
00:03:10,620 --> 00:03:15,170
He interferes with each and every
